file_content.text: They... they're going to get it... please... you've got to stop them....
What happened?
I'll stop them, just tell me who.
Okay, but who?
There's no time... I won't last much longer....
Wow, somebody stomped you good.
You're pretty messed up.
We were on a mission... on our way to the Jedi Temple....
We were ambushed... Imperial scum... you can't let them get it!
Get what? What is it they wanted so badly?
It?
Astrogation charts... top secret... general said... the charts are critical....
Go on.
Imperials got the drop on you? Sloppy.
Pathetic.
A traitor... one of our own... sold us out....
We were sent to get... astrogation charts....
The Imperials know about them... they can't get those charts!
Need some help, huh?
Where are those charts, soldier?
Where are they?
Were there any Sith with the Imperials?
Were Sith involved?
Maybe... I couldn't see... there were too many of them....
Be at peace. I'll take care of everything.
Relax, I'm on it.
Uh-huh. So do these charts happen to be worth anything?
Are they valuable?
Yes... they can't fall into enemy hands. They're top secret....
Doesn't look like you're gonna be rushing off to save the day.
Not much you can do about it.
That's why... that's why you have to....
The old Jedi Temple... top level... in a sealed case, in the Council chambers... that's where the charts are....
Then that's where I'll be going.
I'll head that way.
Be right back.
No... no time....
Should I put you out of your misery before I go?
Need any help dying?
No... I think I might pull through....
The charts... must take them to... General Wendin... Senate tower....
Do it... for the... Republic!
